other along the 150mile border the border is sealed and the only 
communication link is a hot line 
us and soviet forces divided the korean peninsula when they 
ended the japanese occupation at the end of world war ii in 1945 
north korea invaded south korea in 1950 starting the threeyear 
korean war 
